data.title: DART Schedules and Maps
data.meta_description: DART offers a variety of tools to help you get to your destination. Routes are color-coded to help you locate individual routes serving your locations. Information on individual route maps and schedules, our system map, can be found below. Service may vary on holidays.
data.text:
The best way to stay up to date on service alerts and other DART-related news and information is to register for My DART Updates.

Customer Service Information is available 7 days a week : 5 a.m. to 12 a.m.

Holidays: 8 a.m. to 5 p.m.

Closed on Thanksgiving Day and Christmas Day
